spec_data.Name: libdbusmenu
spec_data.Description:
This is a small library designed to make sharing and displaying of menu
structures over DBus simple and easy to use. It works for both QT and GTK+ and
makes building menus simple.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 04 Aug 2017 06:57:46 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Library for passing menus over DBus
